{"tid":96985,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【掟魚落地下】警員+愛協到場調查 拉29歲水族館東主 0 0","createTime":"2017-01-27T10:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T10:10:24.000Z","uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fbbdabcad06e8cfaa24da82001452982cfb7e11","tid":96985,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:10:24.000Z","msg":"旺角一間水族館的東主早前將一條銀龍魚放入充滿氣的膠袋內，並將膠袋連環擲落地以證膠袋十分堅固，片段引來網民一面倒的批評。今日下午2時許，警員及愛護動物協會的職員到場了解事件，警方經初步調查後，相信29歲的負責人曾將一個裝有一條魚的膠袋多次擲向地上，以涉嫌殘酷對待動物將他拘捕，案件交由旺角警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進，該條魚交由相關部門人員跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170126/56227306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170126%2F56227306&d=FplOXDoFoE1lGW4zee4nEH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=81952eff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170126%2F56227306&h=ce95bb2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170126/56227306</a><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求班左膠+動物撚快！打比l愛協去全港酒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}